channel.title: Static IP
channel.description: I go into my Network sharing center and open up my network connections and go into properties and change my 'Internet protocol version 4 (TCP/IPv4) under their properties and when I do that and press ok I am supposed to get a static IP address but instead I just get limited connectivity with my internet, It's like it doesn't let me make a static IP, or at least when I do it just gives me limited connectivity and won't let me on the internet. Has anyone had this problem happen to them before and can anyone help? Thanks Can anyone help?..
